short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Helps you easily navigate Google search results.
short.zh_TW: 用快捷鍵瀏覽谷歌的搜尋結果

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Goocoucou adds vim-like navigation in Google Search Result Page. You can use J/K to go to next or previous search result, and press enter to open selected website. Goocoucou also provides customizable shortcuts and styles. You can now search for anything without using mouse.

Goocoucou is an open source project. I would be happy if you want to contribute to this web extension. And I don't collect user data or do something creepy.

GitHub: https://github.com/FOBshippingpoint/goocoucou-webext

Features:
- Page navigation (H/L for previous/next page)
- Search result navigation (J/K for up/down, press numbers to jump)
- Search result type navigation (Press O to focus on first result type, then press Tab to change focus)
- Customizable shortcuts
- Customizable styles
- Darkmode support
long.zh_TW:
Goocoucou 可以讓你在谷歌搜尋結果頁面使用快捷鍵來瀏覽搜尋結果，你可以按 J/K 來選擇上/下個搜尋結果，按 Enter 開啟網頁。Goocoucou 也提供自訂快捷鍵和外觀風格。現在你可以在手不離鍵的情況下優雅地搜尋任何事物。

Goocoucou 是一個開源專案，歡迎任何人參與貢獻。然後 Goocoucou 不蒐集任何使用者資料或偷偷摸摸地對你的電腦做些怪事。

GitHub: https://github.com/FOBshippingpoint/goocoucou-webext

特色：
- 頁面瀏覽 (H/L 上/下頁)
- 搜尋結果瀏覽 (J/K 上/下個搜尋結果；數字鍵跳至特定結果)
- 切換搜尋結果類型 (按 O 聚焦到第一種搜尋類型，然後按 Tab 切換)
- 可自訂快捷鍵
- 可自訂搜尋結果外觀風格
- 支援深色主題
